replies.body:
I like Taric's stun as a point and click ability it keeps him simple and easy as a champion, yet changing the stun to a Charm would be great and keep the ability mostly how it is, while re-enforcing the fabulousness that is Taric.  Personally this move is his bread and butter followed by the fact that he is known to gives strong auras threw his passive and ult.  Fell like the Embune and the Active on shatter is where he is lacking and can have love added to/rework

Have yall tried adding a ~~ short skip or hop ~~ small beautiful dash to his Shatter ? be kinda cool If it leave a strong speed buff behind him ( Twice as long as the dash? Similar to Flay's Area of effect Range ? ) for *other* champions.  You know cause he inspires and leads those that are not as radiant as him.  Would be nice as a utility tool for engaging or ~~leaving your ADC as fodder~~ helping your Marcksman escape.  Wouldn't be a bad skill to put it on since he loses his own armor buff for using the movement ability.

*  I think one of the most enjoyable moment in league was when I spotted a mobi-boot{{champion:412}}  and {{champion:21}}  POPing ~~Shurelya's~~Talisman by one of our wards and roaming to other between lanes like super fast best buddies. kinda magical. now imagine something like that with Taric.  [Priceless ](http://i.imgur.com/jkFB1iY.png){{champion:44}}
